    },

    "final_verdict": "BIG BALL shows promise as a creative interactive experience but requires significant technical refinement. The project scores well on presentation and creativity but needs improvement in technical implementation and impact definition. Recommendations: 1) Focus on implementing core animation features before expansion, 2) Reduce dependency on third-party tools for better control, 3) Develop more specific use cases and target audiences, 4) Create clearer metrics for success and impact measurement, 5) Consider specialized applications in education or therapy to increase societal impact. The project has potential but needs more development to realize its full vision."
